You might use different mappers

We will consider BWA and Bowtie2
More information about BWA: http://bio-bwa.sourceforge.net/bwa.shtml
More information about bowtie2: http://bowtie-bio.sourceforge.net/bowtie2/manual.shtml

BWA is slower but more accurate than BWA.
BWA mem is more SNP tolerant and also showed the best tolerance to indels.



